Package: icd10am.hfrs
Title: Hospital Frailty Risk Score for ICD-10-AM Coded Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jim", "Pearse", email = "ejpearse@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates the Hospital Frailty Risk Score (HFRS) for Australian admitted patient care data coded using ICD-10-AM, based on the method of Gilbert et al. (2018).
